Generally, all you need to do is dereference the objects - at least, this is the way it is supposed to work. If you are worried about garbage collection, check out [Java SE 6 HotSpot[tm] Virtual Machine Garbage Collection Tuning][5] (or the equivalent document for your JVM version).


