  [2]: http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/awt/Graphics.html#dispose()
  [3]: http://help.eclipse.org/stable/nftopic/org.eclipse.platform.doc.isv/reference/api/org/eclipse/swt/widgets/Widget.html#dispose()
